# VHS tape — counter app from the bootstrap skeleton.
# Render with: `vhs candy-mold/.vhs/start.tape`
Output .vhs/start.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 700
Set Height 240
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Set Theme "Tokyo Night"

Type "./bin/start"
Enter
Sleep 600ms

Up
Sleep 250ms
Up
Sleep 250ms
Up
Sleep 250ms
Up
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 700ms
Type "q"
